text.tspan: Growing up, I have lived in these
Currently I live in LA in California
Hanging out at the local Gamesworkshop store
Eating the best rice dish called Osh
Hanging out with family and friends,
hikes or going dining and wining.
And we are never going to find
the new unless we get a little crazy...
